title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 31
description:
In this video, we will explore this week's new additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace. The marketplace is bustling with mission packs and scenery updates. These updates enhance the scenery for various cities and countries, along with airport upgrades. Moreover, some new aircraft have arrived, and you can also apply one of the numerous livery packs to an aircraft you already own.
